REWARD OFFERED - PLEASE SHARE:  We're partnering with the Florida Department of Law Enforcement and now offering a reward of $6,000 for information leading to the recovery of 14-year-old Jabez Spann.  Anyone with information is asked to call Crime Stoppers of Sarasota tip line at 941-366-TIPS (8477) or 941-316-1201.

Jabez Spann has been missing since September 4, 2017.  He was last seen in the area of 22nd Street in Sarasota wearing a turquoise shirt.  He is a black male, 5’09” and 120 pounds.

In addition to the reward money, the Florida Outdoor Advertising Association is donating digital billboard space in Sarasota County.

If you have any information about the whereabouts of Jabez Spann, please call 941-366-TIPS (8477) or 941-316-1201 or 911.
